        "benefits_kpb6wn": {
          "type": "benefits",
          "settings": {
            "items": "Himalayan pink salt: Highly bioavailable premium sodium source for serious hydration and nerve function.\nDimagnesium malate: A premium, easier-to-absorb magnesium form that supports muscle function and energy.\nOrganic monk fruit extract: Natural sweetness with zero sugar, no stevia, and no sugar alcohols.\nOrganic coconut water powder: Natural electrolytes and minerals for a real-food backbone.\nOrganic bamboo extract: Supports mixability and adds silica to support connective tissues.",
