        "accordion_YdaLfJ": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "border_color": "#171717",
            "hover_color": "#e08fbc",
            "item_1_title": "What's Inside",
            "item_1_content": "<p>~1,000mg sodium for serious sweat replacement, real potassium and magnesium, zero sugar, no maltodextrin, and a flavor system you'll actually finish. Third-party banned substance testing in progress.</p>",
            "item_1_link_text": "View Supplement Facts",
            "item_1_link_url": "shopify://pages/supplement-facts",
            "item_1_open": true,
            "item_2_title": "Why So Much Sodium?",
            "item_2_content": "<p>Because sweat is not just water—it's mostly sodium. Low sodium drinks are fine for light movement. This formula is built for people who actually empty their sweat glands.</p>",
            "item_2_link_text": "",
            "item_2_link_url": "",
            "item_2_open": false,
            "item_3_title": "How to Use",
            "item_3_content": "<p>Add one stick to 16–24 oz cold water. Shake or stir for 5–10 seconds until fully dissolved. Drink before, during, or after training to support hydration and recovery.</p>",
            "item_3_link_text": "",
            "item_3_link_url": "",
            "item_3_open": false,
            "item_4_title": "Who Is This For?",
            "item_4_content": "<p>People who sweat. A lot. Athletes, fighters, endurance runners, hot climate trainers, heavy sweaters, and anyone who has tried hydration products and still felt flat.</p>",
            "item_4_link_text": "",
            "item_4_link_url": "",
            "item_4_open": false,
            "item_5_title": "Preorder Terms",
            "item_5_content": "<p>This is a non-refundable preorder. Limit 1 box per person. Ships late January. Damaged or lost shipments are covered. Your first box is $50 + $4.99 shipping, then you're auto-enrolled in $55/month with free shipping.</p>",
            "item_5_link_text": "View Full Terms",
            "item_5_link_url": "shopify://pages/pre-order-terms",
            "item_5_open": false
          }
        },
        "accordion_Jd6jg4": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "border_color": "#3c3c3c",
            "hover_color": "#c6d76b",
            "item_1_title": "Is it sugar‑free?",
            "item_1_content": "<p>Yes. Our performance electrolytes contain zero sugar and no added sweeteners.</p>",
            "item_1_link_text": "View Supplement Facts",
            "item_1_link_url": "shopify://pages/supplement-facts",
            "item_1_open": false,
            "item_2_title": "Can it be taken by competitive athletes?",
            "item_2_content": "<p>Yes. The formula is designed to be clean, transparent, and tested for banned substances, with third-party testing and lot-level traceability.</p>",
            "item_2_link_text": "",
            "item_2_link_url": "",
            "item_2_open": false,
            "item_3_title": "Can I use it daily?",
            "item_3_content": "<p>If youre sweating enough, yes. It's built for both regular training sessions and high-intensity performance days.</p>",
            "item_3_link_text": "",
            "item_3_link_url": "",
            "item_3_open": false,
            "item_4_title": "Does it contain caffeine?",
            "item_4_content": "<p>No. It’s 100% stimulant‑free.</p>",
            "item_4_link_text": "",
            "item_4_link_url": "",
            "item_4_open": false,
            "item_5_title": "What makes it different from other hydration mixes?",
            "item_5_content": "<p>Athlete‑driven formulation, organic ingredients, US manufacturing, and performance‑level mineral ratios—rather than “lightly flavored water.”</p>",
            "item_5_link_text": "View Full Terms",
            "item_5_link_url": "",
            "item_5_open": false
          }
        }
