    "dw_about_DCiXEE": {
      "type": "dw-about",
      "blocks": {
        "split_NqbM4A": {
          "type": "split",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/dw-sean-00014_21ccc4a6-4c91-42cd-8c6d-00a3eeee58a2.png",
            "image_side": "left",
            "eyebrow": "The doingwell Promise",
            "heading": "Built from a hard lesson",
            "content": "<p>I've spent my whole life chasing performance at the highest level. Early in my UFC career, a drug test came back with a banned substance from a contaminated, non–third-party-tested supplement I trusted. I hadn't cheated, but the system doesn't care what you meant to do.</p><p>doingwell is my response to that. Instead of slapping my name on another label, we built a brand with one internal rule: <strong>if I won't put it in my body, it doesn't go into the product.</strong> Every formula is built for real training, third-party tested, and made for people who care about what goes into their body as much as what they get out of it.</p><p><strong>You're taking something I'm willing to use in camp and on my biggest nights.</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "quote_rjf83W": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "text": "If I won't put it in my body, it doesn't go into the product.",
            "attribution": "",
            "style": "minimal"
